A '''Chief Navigator''' appeared to be a position within the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] military, more specifically within the [[Chiss Expansionary Defense Force]].<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Force Heretic I: Remnant">''[[The New Jedi Order: Force Heretic I: Remnant]]''</ref> One such individual that held this [[Military rank/Legends|rank]] was former [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officer, [[Peita Aabe]].

It was also a position within the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]]. [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Rosion]] held this position aboard ''[[Lusankya/Legends|Lusankya]]'' during the [[Bacta War]].<ref name="X-Wing: The Bacta War">''[[X-Wing: The Bacta War]]''</ref>

